Text: ReThanks for the advice I may be packing casually sheep skin coat jeans sweaters hope that works with our plans Let me know MJ Cant wait to se you TOMORROW Original Message From PATRICIA TLAPEK To Mary Jo Ellen Sent Wednesday October PM Ladies It is predicted that it will be quite cold this weekend pack accordinglydont worry it wont be in the teens T

Hi Kim Here is the info on Sundays festivities Have a great day MJ Original Message From Mary Jo Ellen To Mary Jo Ellen Sent Thursday October AM Subject Last Call for Alcohol There is still room at the Vineyard and on the shuttle We have ten willing winos confirmed for the day but have room for more So grab a friend and join us How can you resist firsthtml Sunday November th am shuttle leaves at am Bay Street between Broderick Baker parking on Baker near Palace of Fine Arts or less per person for shuttle Merlots and a stop for Zinfandel at Seghesio and Food vegetable lasagna chocolate truffles roasted eggplant soup and more MJ Here is a little intro on those confirmed Brad Willmore Hed rather be flying but his second love is wine oh no thats me Liz Lowe Outward Bound Babe After scaling rock walls in Utahs Canyonlands she could really use a drink Lori Mcleese Cuban Cyclist Chic out cycled Castro with Mojito in hand Irene Kuster Tuckus Extraordinaire just ask a WINO Chris McCann The Airforces Finest but he cant talk about it its TOP SECRET shhhhh Whitney Hayes Mini Martha can throw a dinner party like no other did anyone say ENCHILADAS Bernard The Irishman we lied and told him it was a Guinness Sampling Tour Debbie Wong Happy Home Owner Just bought a house in the East Bay and needs to fill up the wine cellar Kyong Merlot Maniac Moving to Coors Country Colorado soon needs to tank up California wine before living in the land of light beer Subject First Weekend in Alexander Valley Marvolous Merlot Sunday November th Thought everyone could use a day drinking wine and enjoying the scenery of the Alexander Valley Wanted to gauge the interest and availability of friends interested in partaking in this winery event There will be complimentary wine tasting and food provided at four vineyards in Alexander Valley Please see the attached website for details firsthtml If there are enough people interested I was thinking of arranging the rental of a party vanshuttle bus for the day Sunday November th from leaving from my house in the Marina After talking with a few limo companies the price per person for limoshuttle service will probably be around for the day Please let me know tomorrow if you are available and interested in participating Please forward this email to others I may have missed on the list too Thanks MJ Mary Jo Ellen SCF Advisors Inc Market
